@(89-95=c565.89) When the king came out from the cloistered lady's presence, each (?) man's heart was dissatisfied. The man who hated his wife left his wife. The man …… his …… abandoned his ……. With elaborate words, with elaborate words, the case of the citizens of @wSN{Adab} was settled. @wDN{Pa-niŋin-ŋara}, their sage, the scholar, the god of @wSN{Adab}, was the scribe.



